biography.bio: André Sjöberg was born on February 9, 1974 in Eskilstuna, Södermanlands län, Sweden as André Thomas Sjöberg. He is an actor and writer, known for As It Is in Heaven (2004), The Border (2011) and Snapphanar (2006).
biography.name: André Sjöberg

biography.bio: Tuva Novotny was born on December 21, 1979 in Stockholm, Sweden as Tuva Moa Matilda Karolina Novotny. She is an actress and director, known for Jalla! Jalla! (2000), Slim Susie (2003) and Dag (2010).
biography.name: Tuva Novotny

biography.bio: Anders Ekborg was born on October 9, 1960 in Stockholm, Sweden. He is an actor, known for Tragique partie de chasse (1999), Happy Christmas! (1999) and Snapphanar (2006).
biography.name: Anders Ekborg

biography.bio: Malin Morgan was born on December 2, 1970 in Kristinehamn, Värmlands län, Sweden. She is known for her work on Slim Susie (2003), God Save the King (2005) and Syndare i sommarsol (2001).
biography.name: Malin Morgan

biography.bio: Gustaf Skarsgård was born on November 12, 1980 in Stockholm, Stockholms län, Sweden as Gustaf Caspar Orm Skarsgård. He is an actor and director, known for Vikings (2013), The Way Back (2010) and Evil (2003).
biography.name: Gustaf Skarsgård

biography.bio: Peter Andersson was born on February 12, 1953 in Gothenburg, Västra Götalands län, Sweden as Ulf Harry Peter Andersson. He is an actor, known for The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (2009), The Girl Who Played with Fire (2009) and Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit (2014).
biography.name: Peter Andersson

biography.bio: Kim Bodnia is an actor who was born in Copenhagen. His ancestry is from Poland and Russia. Kim Bodnia is educated as actor in states of Denmark Copenhagen Theatre school (1988-1991). After a amazing Theatre career as actor and creator of new Danish theatre in Copenhagen, He had His breakthrough as a Movie actor in Nightwatch (1994) for which he received for Best Supporting actor a Robert prize, Danish Film Academy awards and Best actor at the Festival Du Cinema Nordique in Rouen, France. After his breakthrough, he became founder and owner of Bella Entertainment1 Aps and Bella Film Production Aps who have produced his Films since then. In 1996 came Film as Pusher and Kim Bodnia was honoured for his Leads role as Frank. After Pusher he became a Director and Writer and producer of soundtrack. Then followed Films as Bleeder (1999), In China They Eat Dogs (1999), Escape (2001), Dragonfly (2001), Jolly Roger (2001), Old Men in New Cars (2002), Himmelfald (2002), and this was only the beginning of his career as actor, producer, writer, director. In 2010 he was acting in director Sussane Bier's Oscar winner for best Foreign language Film "In A Better World ". In 2011 he became a well known actor in Bollywood Movies for his Role in Aamir Khan's produced film Delhi Belly. In November 2014 he won the The Angela Film Prize Award, at Killkenny Subtitle Film festival in Ireland, for European Film making. Today Kim Bodnia is Worldwide known as actor for his work and role in the Nordic noir Most famous Danish/Swedish Television Crime The Bridge. He Won The Golden Nymph award for best actor in television of year 2014 in Festival de Télévision de Monte-Carlo. Today in cinemas he is known for he role Rosewater in Director Jon Stewart debut film Rosewater.
biography.name: Kim Bodnia

biography.name: Jörgen Persson

biography.bio: Samuel Hellström is an actor, known for Here Is Harold (2014), The Last Waltz (2001) and Call Girl (2012).

biography.bio: Dag Malmberg was born on January 18, 1953 in Gävle, Gävleborgs län, Sweden. He is an actor and director, known for Sjätte dagen (1999), The Bridge (2011) and Easy Money (2010).

biography.bio: Harald Leander is an actor and writer, known for Cirkus Imago (2009), Ronny & Julia (2000) and Cirkus Imago En chans på miljonen (2015).

biography.bio: Jonas Karlström was born in Karlskrona in Blekinge and studied acting at Fridhem's People's University in Svalöv. Living in Malmö he is a freelancing and freewheeling actor currently on a tour with a children's play in his home county of Blekinge, a play he wrote himself. He has taken part in several theatre plays and independent films, such as "The Island" (no, not the Michael Bay film) and "Dödssyndaren". Currently, involved in the play "Tusen och en natt" at the Teater Sagohuset in Lund (Sweden). The play opened on December 29, 2006.
biography.name: Jonas Karlström

biography.bio: Niklas Engdahl was born on September 9, 1974. He is an actor, known for White Trash (2006), Honungsfällan (2008) and Sommaren med Göran (2009).

biography.bio: Admitted to the Malmö Theatre Academy in 1995. Has played at the Royal Dramatic Theatre and Stockholm Stadsteater. Is currently (2002-2003) playing various leads at Malmö Dramatic Theatre.
